Further information
My client, a European global insurer, is looking for a nearly/newly qualified pricing actuary to spearhead the development of their health products and pricing across Asia Pacific. Based in Singapore, the role encompasses product pricing, developing and enhancing existing pricing models and tools, supporting the marketing team, and managing the business` capital requirements. A technically strong and outgoing candidate who is confident building and maintaining client relationships will be an excellent fit. Previous experience in Health product development work highly desirable. Call Merri on +65 6829 7161 or merri.k.a33xyl9w4c@hfg.aptrack.co. EA Licence Number: 13S6608
